/steam/apps/1231670/extras/f301bd573c890a3f24c9c1fc0579bf26.avif?t=1736026877\" width=650 height=450 /></span> <br><br>These creatures are collectively called the Chunkers. The majority of the chunkers adapt to the environment there,<br> but the main character Chunker begins to think of the reasons why they are created and why they have to live in such places.<br><i> “Where did I come from.. and who am I…”</i><br>Chunker opens its eyes within the sewer wastes in the underground of the lab it was abandoned…<br>Will it be possible to escape the dark and brutal underground World…… </i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231670/extras/1fb09c502d0bcd112aec919eaef397f5.poster.avif?t=1736026877\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231670/extras/1fb09c502d0bcd112aec919eaef397f5.webm?t=1736026877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231670/extras/1fb09c502d0bcd112aec919eaef397f5.mp4?t=1736026877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
